settled through DPRK-U.S. talks and that pressure and threats 
will have no effect on the Korean people and may invite 
catastrophe, far from achieving a solution to the problem. 
  Newspapers, news agencies and radios of Italy, Egypt, 
Ethiopia, China, Zaire, Peru, Poland, Nigeria, Austria, Laos and 
