<H3> <TI>   Spokesman: SRV `Prepared' for Rights Talks With U.S. </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK1101131594 Hong Kong AFP in English 1303 GMT 11 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> BK1101131594 </F>
<F P=104>  Hong Kong AFP </F>


