Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Vientiane, January 10 (KPL) -- A 10-kw radio 
transceiver is now put on operation in the province of 
Champassak after one month of installation. 
  The medium-wave radio system was set up under the assistance 
of a Chinese economic and technical cooperation company. 
  The hand-over of the broadcasting facility took place on 
December 31. 

