<DOCNO> FBIS3-47333 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreas008__a94021" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EAS-94-008-A </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  12 January 1994 </DATE1>

