<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, January 11 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- On the 
occasion of scheduled exploitation of the oil "Tsagaan Els" 
deposit in the region of Zuunbayan on the territory of the 
Dornogobi Aimak the director of the Mongolian Petroleum Company 
has applied with an official letter to the head of the local 
administration. The letter contains a request not to allow the 
wasting of the pipes and equipment having been applied at the 
enterprise acting there earlier. Meanwhile just for the last 
year from here there has been taken away out of the country 
through the southern border several dozens of trucks with metal. 

