Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] This morning, the Office of the Presidency held a 
press conference to introduce a presidential order on the 
promulgation of the Law on Environmental Protection, the Law on 
Business Bankruptcy, the Law on Amendment, and the Supplement to 
the Law on the Organization of People's Courts which were passed 
