  [Text] Pyongyang, January 13 (KCNA) -- The spokesman of the 
General Federation of National Peasants Associations of South 
Korea (Chonnong) at a recent press conference denounced traitor 
Kim Yong- sam's policy of killing farmers, according to a report 
of a South Korean newspaper. 
  He said Kim Yong-sam's promise in his election "commitments" 
