  Noting that Kim Yong-sam, disclosing his true color, has 
taken today the road of totally sacrificing agriculture and 
farmers with the measure of rice market opening, he declared 
that Chonnong would resolutely turn out in the struggle to 
defend "our rice, our agriculture". 

