  [Text] U.S. Under Secretary of State Joan E. Spero, who is 
currently visiting Japan, gave an interview in Tokyo on 12 
January. Touching on the Japan-U.S. framework trade talks, Spero 
stated: "No progress has been noted in the talks on different 
sectors. It seems that there are situations in which Prime 
